How to create the project stepwise.
1>npm init.
2>npm i express.
3>npm i mongoose.
4>npm i nodemon.
5>npm i hbs.
Make Directory/folder.
5>mkdir src.
6>add file app.js in src folder.                type nul > app.js.
7>Add database folder in src directory.         mkdir db.
8>Add Models folder in src directory.           mkdir models.
9>Add conn.js file in db directory.


Add this in package.json / debug.  
"dev" : "nodemon src/app.js -e js,hbs"